<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KHUARUAHHAR KHAMHTU CH108</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sualthlahnak kha Khrih nih a ser, Khuaruahhar ngaingai a si! Ka
 sualthlahnak man kha a pek, Khamhnak khuaruahhar a si!

[C1]
   Khuaruahharnak kha Jesuh a si, Maw ka Jesuh, Khuaruahharnak kha
   Jesuh a si, Ka Bawipa.

[V2]
 Ka lungchung sualnak a thianter, Khuaruahhar Khamhbawi a si! Keimah he
 a kal ti zungzal, Nifatin a kan zohkhenh!

[C2]
   Khuaruahharnak kha Jesuh a si, Maw ka Jesuh, Khuaruahharnak kha
   Jesuh a si, Ka Bawipa.

[V3]
 A thiang thi kha a thlet ca ah, Amah ka thangthat theo lai. Ka thlarau
 kha a dawt ca ah, Pathian sin a phakpi lai,

[C3]
   Khuaruahharnak kha Jesuh a si, Maw ka Jesuh, Khuaruahharnak kha
   Jesuh a si, Ka Bawipa.

[V4]
 Teinak thazang kha a ka pek, Khuaruahhar Khamhbawi a si, Ka lung Amah
 sin ka pek lai, Vawlei zeihmanh ruat loin.

[C4]
   Khuaruahharnak kha Jesuh a si, Maw ka Jesuh, Khuaruahharnak kha
   Jesuh a si, Ka Bawipa.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<hymn_number>108</hymn_number>
</song>